/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/prices-drop-as-international-airlines-resume-flights-to-israel/0000018c-f95d-dd94-a9cc-fbfd0b7c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列冰球联合会向体育仲裁法院提出上诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-ice-hockey-federation-appeals-to-court-of-arbitration-for-sport/0000018c-f949-dd94-a9cc-fbed46f70000</link><description>在 U20 男子世界锦标赛举行前 12 天，国际冰球联合会宣布禁止以色列参加比赛，“出于对所有参赛者安全的担忧” ■ 以色列称这一决定是“反犹太主义”，并向 CAS 提出上诉</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 17:37:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-ice-hockey-federation-appeals-to-court-of-arbitration-for-sport/0000018c-f949-dd94-a9cc-fbed46f70000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡支持本格维尔，表示以色列监狱长不会延长任期</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/backing-ben-gvir-netanyahu-says-israels-prison-chief-wont-have-term-extended/0000018c-f95d-d517-af9d-fd7f92de0000</link><description>尽管战时内阁同意不改变像她这样的高级职位，但凯蒂·佩里作为最高监狱长的任期预计将于一月下旬结束</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:43:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/backing-ben-gvir-netanyahu-says-israels-prison-chief-wont-have-term-extended/0000018c-f95d-d517-af9d-fd7f92de0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部阿拉伯城市汽车爆炸 男子丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/man-killed-in-car-explosion-in-arab-city-in-central-israel/0000018c-f94d-dd94-a9cc-fbed31050000</link><description>蒂拉发生大规模爆炸，导致一名 30 多岁男子丧生，这是本周这座阿拉伯城市发生的第二起凶杀案</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/man-killed-in-car-explosion-in-arab-city-in-central-israel/0000018c-f94d-dd94-a9cc-fbed31050000</guid></item><item><title>艾曼·奥德仍然相信两国解决方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ayman-odeh-still-believes-in-the-two-state-solution/0000018c-f3f1-da04-a7df-f3f54f5a0000</link><description>艾曼·奥德 (Ayman Odeh) 16 岁时，被辛​​贝特 (Shin Bet) 安全部门叫去进行一系列关于他的政治活动的谈话。 40 多岁时，他是以色列犹太人最喜欢的阿拉伯政治家。现在他退出政党政治，但这并不是因为他放弃了更美好未来的梦想</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 16:25:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ayman-odeh-still-believes-in-the-two-state-solution/0000018c-f3f1-da04-a7df-f3f54f5a0000</guid></item><item><title>与真主党的战争是不可避免的。但以色列应该发起这一行动吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/a-war-with-hezbollah-is-inevitable-but-should-israel-initiate-it/0000018c-f7d5-d432-a7ae-fffdf0e50000</link><description>以色列现在应对真主党及其挑衅有重要的战略理由。但黎巴嫩战争可能会将美国自由派选民中不断高涨的反以色列情绪转变为一场完美风暴。这将是一场以色列从未经历过的冲突</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 15:45:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-11/ty-article-opinion/.premium/a-war-with-hezbollah-is-inevitable-but-should-israel-initiate-it/0000018c-f7d5-d432-a7ae-fffdf0e50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列男子被控刺伤妻子、打伤儿子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-charged-with-stabbing-and-killing-wife-wounding-son/0000018c-f902-df8a-adbf-fb7eb4260000</link><description>起诉书指控 Asher Bohbot 对其 15 岁的儿子犯有严重谋杀罪和严重殴打罪，当时儿子在事件中试图阻止他。一位家人的熟人表示，布布特以前殴打过他的妻子，她曾考虑与他离婚</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 15:22:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-charged-with-stabbing-and-killing-wife-wounding-son/0000018c-f902-df8a-adbf-fb7eb4260000</guid></item><item><title>从被毁坏的家中撤离后，来自加沙边境的以色列孩子在特拉维夫重新开始学校</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/evacuated-from-a-devastated-home-israeli-kids-from-gaza-border-restart-school-in-tel-aviv/0000018c-f8e3-dd94-a9cc-faef01000000</link><description>大约三周前，大约 400 名雷伊姆居民从最南端城市埃拉特的酒店房间收拾行李，他们在 10 月 7 日袭击事件后从家中撤离后一直住在那里，开始了生活的新篇章。这次是在特拉维夫的赫茨尔街</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 15:11:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/evacuated-from-a-devastated-home-israeli-kids-from-gaza-border-restart-school-in-tel-aviv/0000018c-f8e3-dd94-a9cc-faef01000000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院驳回内塔尼亚胡违反利益冲突协议的请愿书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-rejects-petition-saying-netanyahu-broke-conflict-of-interest-deal/0000018c-f89c-d30b-a59d-f8de8e6f0000</link><description>“据我们所知，自10月7日以来，以色列一直处于战争状态，这对我们面前的案件产生了重大影响。在这些影响中，作为请愿者主张核心的立法程序目前并未得到推进，”高等法院法官说</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 14:56:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-rejects-petition-saying-netanyahu-broke-conflict-of-interest-deal/0000018c-f89c-d30b-a59d-f8de8e6f0000</guid></item><item><title>“南非是哈马斯的合法机构”：以色列谴责国际法院加沙种族灭绝听证会“扭曲”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-is-hamas-legal-arm-israel-blasts-distorted-icj-gaza-genocide-hearing/0000018c-f898-d30b-a59d-f8dec5b30000</link><description>以色列外交部发言人称南非律师为“哈马斯”代表，周五第二天听证会前已做出初步回应</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 14:35:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-is-hamas-legal-arm-israel-blasts-distorted-icj-gaza-genocide-hearing/0000018c-f898-d30b-a59d-f8dec5b30000</guid></item><item><title>汗尤尼斯的“720度”战斗，可能决定以色列与哈马斯战争的结果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/fighting-in-720-degrees-in-khan-yunis-where-what-happens-may-decide-outcome-of-war/0000018c-f881-dd94-a9cc-faed2e6f0000</link><description>双桅船。驻扎在加沙地带南部的以色列陆军第 98 师指挥官丹·戈德福斯 (Dan Goldfus) 将军每天都在解决像魔方一样的问题，因为他监督着一支在地面、空中和哈马斯隧道中行动的臃肿部队</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 14:10:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/fighting-in-720-degrees-in-khan-yunis-where-what-happens-may-decide-outcome-of-war/0000018c-f881-dd94-a9cc-faed2e6f0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列政府意图消灭加沙的巴勒斯坦人”：南非向国际法院提出种族灭绝案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/israeli-govt-is-intent-on-destroying-palestinians-south-africa-presents-genocide-case/0000018c-f8bc-d517-af9d-fcbe87ae0000</link><description>南非法律团队在海牙进行了开庭陈词，指责以色列的种族灭绝行为、言论和煽动行为。他们引用了内塔尼亚胡总理、赫尔佐格总统和几位部长的声明作为证据。以色列将于周五针对这些指控为自己辩护</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 13:49:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/israeli-govt-is-intent-on-destroying-palestinians-south-africa-presents-genocide-case/0000018c-f8bc-d517-af9d-fcbe87ae0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔否认哈马斯领导人流亡条款，以色列回应新的人质释放提案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/qatar-denies-hamas-leaders-clause-as-israel-responds-to-new-hostage-release-proposal/0000018c-f87b-d517-af9d-fc7f5e340000</link><description>政治消息人士强调，以色列的一贯立场不是同意哈马斯停止战争的要求，也不是以完全停止在加沙地带的军事活动为前提达成释放人质协议</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 13:21:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/qatar-denies-hamas-leaders-clause-as-israel-responds-to-new-hostage-release-proposal/0000018c-f87b-d517-af9d-fc7f5e340000</guid></item><item><title>1986年以来失踪士兵的女儿罗恩·阿拉德：以色列政界人士必须就释放人质进行谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/daughter-of-soldier-missing-since-1986-israel-must-negotiate-for-hostages-release/0000018c-f7d0-d432-a7ae-fff972390000</link><description>尤瓦尔·阿拉德在脸书上写道，“因为历史不仅在我眼前重演，而且人们似乎拒绝从历史中吸取教训”，并警告应立即将人质带回家</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 12:10:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/daughter-of-soldier-missing-since-1986-israel-must-negotiate-for-hostages-release/0000018c-f7d0-d432-a7ae-fff972390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列科技行业的情况会变得更糟吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/can-things-get-even-worse-for-israel-tech/0000018c-f860-dd94-a9cc-faecd27d0000</link><description>去年是初创国家有史以来最糟糕的一年。现在，2024 年将会出现更多战争、腐败政府和持续的全球经济衰退</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 12:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/can-things-get-even-worse-for-israel-tech/0000018c-f860-dd94-a9cc-faecd27d0000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列人因玩枪误杀朋友而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/three-israelis-arrested-for-accidentally-killing-friend-after-toying-with-gun/0000018c-f796-d365-a3ce-f7f67c720000</link><description>自以色列国家安全部降低申请和领取持枪许可证的条件以来，已发生多起涉枪伤亡事件</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 10:05:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/three-israelis-arrested-for-accidentally-killing-friend-after-toying-with-gun/0000018c-f796-d365-a3ce-f7f67c720000</guid></item><item><title>枪械如何成为以色列必备的时尚潮流</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/biggest-fashion-trend-in-israel-in-2024-firearms/0000018c-f3dd-d6ce-abcc-fbdf22600000</link><description>以色列与哈马斯战争爆发以来，枪支已经从一种防护手段转变为一种身份象征和宣言</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 09:15:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/biggest-fashion-trend-in-israel-in-2024-firearms/0000018c-f3dd-d6ce-abcc-fbdf22600000</guid></item><item><title>“南非是哈马斯的合法机构”：以色列谴责国际法院种族灭绝听证会“扭曲”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-live/intl-court-of-justice-unlikely-to-order-gaza-cease-fire-israeli-officials-say/0000018c-f711-d432-a7ae-fff9faed0000</link><description>海牙国际法院听取了南非的指控，指控以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝，但未能惩罚煽动种族灭绝的人。检方援引总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡、总统艾萨克·赫尔佐格和以色列部长的声明作为种族灭绝意图的证据。以色列将于周五针对这些指控为自己辩护</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 06:13:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-live/intl-court-of-justice-unlikely-to-order-gaza-cease-fire-israeli-officials-say/0000018c-f711-d432-a7ae-fff9faed0000</guid></item></channel></rss>